                      "html": "<p>I hereby consent to the disclosure of information from my income tax records, by the Canada Revenue Agency to an official of the Ministry of Post-Secondary Education and Future Skills, that pertains to information provided on any StudentAid BC application. The information disclosed will be relevant to, and used solely for the purpose of, determining and verifying eligibility for student aid under the Canada Student Financial Assistance Act. The information disclosed by the Canada Revenue Agency to the Ministry of Post-Secondary Education and Future Skills will be protected from unauthorized use or disclosure and will not be disclosed to any other person or organization without my approval. This authorization is valid for the two taxation years prior to the year of signature of this consent, and the year of signature.</p>\n",
